    <link href="http://finatra.info/finatra/blog/2015/06/13/announcing-2nd-milestone-release-of-finatra-2-dot-0-0/"/>
    <updated>2015-06-13T09:32:08-07:00</updated>
    <id>http://finatra.info/finatra/blog/2015/06/13/announcing-2nd-milestone-release-of-finatra-2-dot-0-0</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h4>We&rsquo;re pleased to announce the <a href="https://github.com/twitter/finatra/releases/tag/v2.0.0.M2">second milestone release</a> of Finatra 2.0.0!</h4>

<p>You can download the release from <a href="http://search.maven.org/#search%7Cga%7C1%7Cg%3A%22com.twitter.finatra%22%20AND%20v%3A%222.0.0.M2%22">Maven Central</a>.</p>

<p>For a full list of changes and updates see the diff <a href="https://github.com/twitter/finatra/compare/v2.0.0.M1...v2.0.0.M2">here</a>.</p>

<h4>Features:</h4>

<ul>
<li>We&rsquo;ve updated and added to the example projects including:

<ul>
<li>A Typesafe <a href="https://github.com/twitter/finatra/tree/master/examples/finatra-activator-seed">activator template</a> for getting started with a Finatra project using <a href="https://www.typesafe.com/community/core-tools/activator-and-sbt">Activator</a>.</li>
<li>An <a href="https://github.com/twitter/finatra/tree/master/examples/finatra-hello-world-heroku">example project</a> that shows how to configure and run a Finatra application on <a href="https://www.heroku.com/">Heroku</a>.</li>
<li>An example <a href="http://maven.apache.org/">Maven</a> pom.xml in <a href="https://github.com/twitter/finatra/blob/master/examples/finatra-hello-world/pom.xml">finatra-hello-world</a> for building a Finatra application with Maven.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>


<p>See the Finatra <a href="https://github.com/twitter/finatra">github page</a> for more information on getting started.</p>

<p>&ndash; The <a href="https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/finatra-users">Finatra</a> Team</p>
]]></content>
