  <entry>
    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Announcing First Milestone Release of Finatra 2.0.0 &mdash; ~50x Faster Than v1.6.0!]]></title>
    <link href="http://finatra.info/finatra/blog/2015/04/30/announcing-first-milestone-release-of-finatra-2-dot-0-0/"/>
    <updated>2015-04-30T14:05:13-07:00</updated>
    <id>http://finatra.info/finatra/blog/2015/04/30/announcing-first-milestone-release-of-finatra-2-dot-0-0</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h4>We&rsquo;re pleased to announce the first milestone release of Finatra 2.0.0!</h4>

<p>You can download the release from <a href="http://search.maven.org/#search%7Cga%7C1%7Cg%3A%22com.twitter.finatra%22">Maven Central</a>.</p>

<h4>Features:</h4>

<ul>
<li>Significant performance improvements over v1.6.0.</li>
<li>Powerful feature and integration test support.</li>
<li>JSR-330 Dependency Injection using <a href="https://github.com/google/guice">Google Guice</a>.</li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/FasterXML/jackson">Jackson</a> based JSON parsing with additional support for required fields, default values, and custom validations.</li>
<li><a href="http://logback.qos.ch/">Logback</a> <a href="http://logback.qos.ch/manual/mdc.html">MDC</a> integration with <a href="https://github.com/twitter/util/blob/master/util-core/src/main/scala/com/twitter/util/Local.scala">com.twitter.util.Local</a> for contextual logging across futures.</li>
</ul>


<p>See the Finatra <a href="https://github.com/twitter/finatra">github page</a> for more information on getting started.</p>

<p>&ndash; The <a href="https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/finatra-users">Finatra</a> Team</p>
]]></content>
