    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Finatra 1.6.0 Released]]></title>
    <link href="http://finatra.info/finatra/blog/2015/01/09/finatra-1-dot-6-0-released/"/>
    <updated>2015-01-09T03:00:00-08:00</updated>
    <id>http://finatra.info/finatra/blog/2015/01/09/finatra-1-dot-6-0-released</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3>Last release for 1.x.x and Scala 2.9</h3>

<p><p class="lead">
As we prepare for the upcoming 2.x.x release, this will be the last 1.x.x release
and also the last release to be published for scala 2.9.x.</p>

<h3>New Finatra and Maintainer!</h3>

<p><p class="lead">
I&rsquo;m happy to announce that <a href="https://twitter.com/scosenza">Steve Cosenza</a> will be
taking over the project for the 2.x.x release and beyond. We&rsquo;re excited to release
the next major iteration of Finatra and share everything we&rsquo;ve learned using it in
production at <a href="https://twitter.com">Twitter</a> over the course of a year.</p>

<p><br/></p>

<h3>Changelog</h3>

<p><p class="lead">
<a href="https://github.com/twitter/finatra/commit/d90c77dbd09fb74abacb437258f1d60bf92efd8d">d90c77</a> Can use ChannelBuffer&rsquo;s as Response</p>

<p><p class="lead">
<a href="https://github.com/twitter/finatra/commit/d73cbbf644f58ed1dd756f186b1e272e31b0ae39">d73cbb</a>, <a href="https://github.com/twitter/finatra/commit/8192716f00ae513358d1210645e4e47352be8e48">819271</a> Fix controller-specific ErrorHandler&rsquo;s</p>

<p><p class="lead">
<a href="https://github.com/twitter/finatra/commit/129184a90f4255a97e2983407b324747f8c218e4">129184</a> Fixed Heroku Deployments</p>

<p><p class="lead">
<a href="https://github.com/bpfoster/finatra/commit/04b5cbb9e71488d590eab76cffcc284685cbaa47">04b5cb</a> 2 Way SSL support</p>

<p><p class="lead">
<a href="https://github.com/twitter/finatra/commit/fcce1669c3b2e5a14d7a242db64b226f8be3b73b">fcce16</a> Quieter errors in the logs</p>

<p><p class="lead">
<a href="https://github.com/twitter/finatra/commit/33b1063d4c59d8ea82dc37f176484cde64f26bc8">33b106</a> Asset Directory browser! set com.twitter.finatra.showDirectories=true to enable</p>

<p><p class="lead">
<a href="https://github.com/twitter/finatra/commit/2edd33df0bd5a5be4d6161b7c8bd53954593939f">2edd33</a> Clean up build files, lock to twitter-server 1.7.3</p>

<p><p class="lead">
<a href="https://github.com/twitter/finatra/commit/982703ab79900d6a0e2ab7d6ff039accf0723979">982703</a> Remove scalatest dependency from jar, must now depend on it yourself</p>

<p><br/></p>

<h4>SBT</h4>

<p><figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='scala'><span class='line'><span class="s">&quot;com.twitter&quot;</span> <span class="o">%%</span> <span class="s">&quot;finatra&quot;</span> <span class="o">%</span> <span class="s">&quot;1.6.0&quot;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>

<h4>Maven</h4>

<p><figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
